---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy Policy for Plus44 apps including Pass Australian Citizenship Test.">
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <article class="prose prose-gray max-w-none">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-[#0c7f38] mt-8 mb-4">Pass Australian Citizenship Test</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-500 mb-8"><strong>Last updated:</strong> 4 February 2026</p>

        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Andrew Downing (Plus44.xyz) ("we", "our", or "us") operates the mobile application Pass Australian Citizenship Test (the "App").
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          This Privacy Policy explains how information is collected, used, and disclosed when you use our App.
        </p>

        <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200" />

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>

        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">a) Information You Provide</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          We do not require you to create an account or provide personal information such as your name, email address, or phone number to use the App.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">b) Automatically Collected Information</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          We collect limited technical information via Amplitude Analytics for the purpose of understanding how the App is used and improving performance.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-2">This may include:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-1">
          <li>Anonymous user identifier</li>
          <li>Device type (e.g. iPhone model)</li>
          <li>App usage events (e.g. which screens are viewed)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-2">We do not collect:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-1">
          <li>Your name</li>
          <li>Your email address</li>
          <li>Your precise location</li>
          <li>Your contacts</li>
          <li>Any biometric or health data</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">c) Payments</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          All payments are processed securely by Apple's In-App Purchase system. We do not receive or store your payment or billing details.
        </p>

        <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200" />

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">2. How We Use Information</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-2">We use collected information to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-1">
          <li>Improve app performance and usability</li>
          <li>Understand feature usage</li>
          <li>Fix bugs and optimize user experience</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          We do not use your data for advertising, profiling, or selling to third parties.
        </p>

        <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200" />

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">3. Data Sharing</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-2">We only share limited data with:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-1">
          <li>Amplitude Analytics (for usage analytics)</li>
          <li>Apple (for subscription and payment processing)</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal data.
        </p>

        <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200" />

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">4. Data Retention</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Analytics data is retained only as long as necessary for product improvement and diagnostics.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          You may reset your anonymous identifier by reinstalling the App.
        </p>

        <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200" />

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">5. Data Security</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          We implement reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect your data. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure.
        </p>

        <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200" />

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">6. Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          The App is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children.
        </p>

        <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200" />

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">7. Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-2">
          Depending on your jurisdiction (including Australia, GDPR, and CCPA), you may have the right to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-1">
          <li>Request access to data</li>
          <li>Request deletion of data</li>
          <li>Object to processing</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          You can exercise these rights by contacting us.
        </p>

        <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200" />

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">8. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-2">We use:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-600 mb-4 space-y-1">
          <li>Amplitude Analytics – <a href="https://amplitude.com/privacy" class="text-[#5CE1E6] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://amplitude.com/privacy</a></li>
          <li>Apple In-App Purchases – <a href="https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/" class="text-[#5CE1E6] hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/</a></li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Their privacy policies apply independently.
        </p>

        <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200" />

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
          We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page.
        </p>

        <hr class="my-8 border-gray-200" />

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">10. Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-2">
          If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy:
        </p>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-6 mt-4">
          <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Andrew Downing (Plus44.xyz)</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Email: <a href="mailto:support@plus44.xyz" class="text-[#5CE1E6] hover:underline">support@plus44.xyz</a></p>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Website: <a href="https://plus44.xyz" class="text-[#5CE1E6] hover:underline">https://plus44.xyz</a></p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
